      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 4 Business Day article about decline in value of Euro</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day on May 4 about the decline in the value of the euro omitted the source of remarks made by Ernst Welteke, president of Germany's central bank, and reported by Bloomberg News. Mr. Welteke, who doubted that intervention to prop up the currency would be successful, was interviewed by Market News International.</p>
      </block>
